model.control:
$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT RATE DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2

$DATA      C:\Workspace\Example5/dataWithPeriod.csv IGNORE=@

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IOVV = 0  
  TVV2=THETA(1)   *CAGE**THETA(7)   *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))   
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3) *CWTKGONE**THETA(8)  *CCRCL**THETA(9)  *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) 

  K=CL/V2      
  K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)  
  D1=THETA(10) *EXP(ETA(4)) ; infusion only    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F +EPS(1)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA      
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR    
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  (0,0.1) 	; THETA(6) K23~WT 	 ; init for K23~WT    


  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(7) POWER volume ~AGE  

  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(8) POWER clearance~WT  

  (-4,-0.2) 	; THETA(9) POWER clearance~CRCL 

  (0.01,0.2) 		;; THETA(10) D1  
$OMEGA    
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  
$OMEGA BLOCK(2) ;; block OMEGA block 
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1
  0.01 0.1 		;; ETA(5) ETA ON D1   
  ;; no iov ON CL
  ;; no iov ON V
$SIGMA   
  200 	; EPS(1) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R

;; Phenotype

  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(9) POWER clearance~AGE

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN2 ;; advan2 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE

  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)  
  TVV2=THETA(1)      *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))   
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)  *CAGE**THETA(4)   *EXP(IOVCL)

  D1=THETA(6)    
  TVKA=THETA(2)

  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR

  (0.001,0.1,1) ;;THETA(6) D1

  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE

  0.1

  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO

  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4)

  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K32=THETA(5)  
  ALAG1=THETA(9)
  ;; No D1    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS

  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR    
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23

  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2

$OMEGA    
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA   
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(6) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(7)  
  TVV2=THETA(1)      *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))

  TVCL= THETA(3)  *CAGE**THETA(6)   *EXP(IOVCL)

  K32=THETA(5)  
  ALAG1=THETA(7)
  D1=THETA(8)*EXP(ETA(4))    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS

  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR

  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32

  (0.001,0.1,1) ;;THETA(8) D1

  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  
$OMEGA ;;  
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON D1 		;; D1 and lag, block

$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(5)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(7)
$SIGMA   
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)  
  TVV2=THETA(1) *CWTKGONE**THETA(7) *EXP(SEX*THETA(8))    *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))   
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)     *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) 

  K=CL/V2      
  K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)  
  ALAG1=THETA(9)
  ;; No D1    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA      
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR    
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  (0,0.1) 	; THETA(6) K23~WT 	 ; init for K23~WT    
  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(7) POWER volume ~WT    
  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(8) EXPONENTIAL volume~SEX    






  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(9) ALAG1   
$OMEGA    
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA   
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IOVV = 0  
  TVV2=THETA(1) *EXP(CWTKGZERO*THETA(6)) *EXP(SEX*THETA(7)) *CAGE**THETA(8)   *EXP(IOVV)

  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3) *EXP(CWTKGZERO*THETA(9)) *CAGE**THETA(10) *CCRCL**THETA(11)  *EXP(IOVCL)

  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)  
  ALAG1=THETA(12)
  ;; No D1    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F +EPS(1)
  Y=IOBS

  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L

  (0.001,20)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23

  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume~SEX    
  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(8) POWER volume ~AGE

  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(10) POWER clearance~AGE  
  (-4,-0.2) 	; THETA(11) POWER clearance~CRCL

  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  
$OMEGA ;;  
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON D1

  ;; no iov ON V

  200 	; EPS(1) additive error

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)  
  TVV2=THETA(1) *CWTKGONE**THETA(6)   *EXP(COV2*THETA(7))  *EXP(IOVV)

  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)  
  ALAG1=THETA(10)
  ;; No D1    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA      
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR    
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  ; init for K23~WT    
  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(6) POWER volume ~WT    


  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 
  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(8) POWER clearance~WT  
  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(9) POWER clearance~AGE  


  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(10) ALAG1   
$OMEGA    
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA   
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

;; OrderedDict([('ADVAN', 1), ('K23~WT', 0), ('KAETA', 1), ('V2~WT', 1), ('V2~AGE', 0), ('V2~SEX', 0), ('V2~COV2', 1), ('CL~WT', 0), ('CL~AGE', 1), ('CL~CRCL', 0), ('CL~COV1', 0), ('IOVCL', 1), ('IOVV', 0), ('INITCL', 0), ('ETAD1LAG', 2), ('D1LAG', 0), ('RESERR', 0)])
;; Genotype

;; Num non-influential tokens = 0

$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT DROP DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2

$DATA      C:\Workspace\Example5/dataWithPeriod.csv IGNORE=@

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 
$PK      
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(6) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(7)  
  TVV2=THETA(1) *CWTKGONE**THETA(6)   *EXP(COV2*THETA(7))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))   
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)  *CAGE**THETA(8)   *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) 

  K=CL/V2      
  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)  
  ALAG1=THETA(9)*EXP(ETA(4))
  ;; No D1    
  TVKA=THETA(2) 
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3))     
  S2 = V2 
$ERROR     	
  REP = IREP      
  IPRED =F  
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA      
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR    
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  ; init for K23~WT    
  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(6) POWER volume ~WT    


  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 

  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(8) POWER clearance~AGE  


  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(9) ALAG1   
$OMEGA    
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME  
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA  
$OMEGA ;; 3rd OMEGA block 
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1 
  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(5)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(7)
$SIGMA   
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error
